# Example when while is better than for in Python
## 啟發來源是leetcode的 [387. First Unique Character in a String](https://leetcode.com/problems/first-unique-character-in-a-string)

## Version：For
```python
def firstUniqChar(s):
    if len(s) == 0:
        return -1
    for i,c in enumerate(s):
        if s.count(c) == 1:
            return i
    return -1
```
## Version：While
```python
def firstUniqChar(s):
    if len(s) == 0:
        return -1
    s1 = s
    while len(s1) > 0:
        if s1.count(s1[0]) == 1:
            return s.find(s1[0])
        s1 = s1.replace(s1[0],"")
    return -1
```
## 這次使用的例子為長度`16937` 的 string `s`
```python
s = ""
```
## For 和 While 在`迴圈次數`上的差異甚大
